1. Configure your NIC with IP Address as 192.168.3.1
2. DHCP server binds itself with INADDR_ANY
3. DHCP Server starts assigining IP address to DHCP client from 192.168.3.2
4. This DHCP Server has been tested on Linux Kernel on Ubuntu Machine
5. For any issue please report it to NAUSHAD.DLN@GMAIL.COM

